  "details": "This package includes the mkimage program, which allows generation of U-Boot images in various formats, and the fw_printenv and fw_setenv programs to read and modify U-Boot's environment.\r\n\r\nSecurity Fix(es):\r\n\r\nIn Das U-Boot through 2022.07-rc5, an integer signedness error and resultant stack-based buffer overflow in the &quot;i2c md&quot; command enables the corruption of the return address pointer of the do_i2c_md function.(CVE-2022-34835)",
